precis:
PASSOVER PRODUCTS REMISSION ORDER - which provides: (a) for the remission
of various duties and taxes payable on Passover holiday foods and products
of a class not available in Canada; and (b) for the revocation of Order in
Council P.C. 1966-19/2220 of December 1, 1966.
